description:
The Keebler Company presents DC Comics' The New Teen Titans is in cooperation with The President's Drug Awareness Campaign. Speedy and the Titans explore Drug addiction. Part of the Drug awareness campaign. Originally a promotional comic, but was so popular it became a fund raiser issue (the issue with the price and the black box at the bottom).

Starfire's costume was altered and Robin (Dick Grayson) was replaced by The Protector because of license issues.
name: Plague!

volume.name: The New Teen Titans (Drug Abuse Awareness)

description: The second installment of the New Teen Titans' drug awareness campaign. Starfire's costume had to be changed and Robin (Dick Grayson) was replaced with the Protector, because Robin was licensed to another company.
name: Battle!

volume.name: The New Teen Titans (Drug Abuse Awareness)

description: The third installment of the Drug awareness New Teen Titian comics. Starfire's costume was altered and Robin (Dick Grayson) was replaced with the Protector because of licensing issues.
name: Problem Child

volume.name: The New Teen Titans (Drug Abuse Awareness)

description: Beginning a new era in Dungeons & Dragonshistory! The genre-defining roleplaying game gets its first ongoing series in more than 20 years! Join writer John Rogers (Blue Beetle ) and artist Andrea Di Vito (Annihilation ) as they bring us a tale of high adventure and deep secrets. Adric Fell leads a band of heroes in a world where civilization has been reduced to a few scattered points of light amid a rising tide of shadows.
name: Shadowplague, Part One: Bad Day

description: Jason Todd has seemingly come back from the dead as Gotham's newest vigilante and his violent ways pit him against the Dark Knight - but not before Jason takes hostage the very person responsible for his death: The Joker! Collecting the stories of the Red Hood from Batman #645-650 and Batman Annual #25!
name: Volume Two
Possession is Nine-Tenths of the Flaw
The Secret of the Old Meal
You Can't Get There From Here
The Night is Dark and I am Far From Homeroom

description:
Morgana La Fay reveals her hand as she sends out a ruined army to conquer England in her name. And the only one standing in her way is Avatar. But how can even a God cast in human form fight magic?

It's do or die for 'A Knight to Dismember.'Â  Â  Â
name: Something Wicked This Way Comes

description: Chicago, 1930. Mobsters! Hijacked lab equipment! Mystery Men! Gunfights! Car chases! A mad scientist's machines, machinations, and the conspiracy behind it all! Tesla too! And that's just in the first issue ATOMIC ROBO AND THE DEADLY ART OF SCIENCE!
name: The Man with Two Skulls

volume.name: Atomic Robo and the Deadly Art of Science

description: The invasion of the "New Kids" continues with PART FOUR... and this time the joke's on Reggie as he matches wits with a mysterious new prankster! Meanwhile, Jughead somehow attracts a twittering female fan club while Ethel discovers a previously hidden talent that has the new kids all atwitter!
name: New Kids Off The Wall, Part 4: Prankenstein and the Twitters
